author: Rsx11m
title: SeaMonkey/StatusMeetings
text:
Difference between revisions of "SeaMonkey/StatusMeetings" From MozillaWiki (added link to 2016-11-08 page) Latest revision as of 07:28, 5 November 2016 Resources Discussion Suiterunner 
Status meetings for SeaMonkey are scheduled biweekly on Tuesdays at 13:00 UTC in the #seamonkey channel on IRC. This corresponds to 14:00 CET (Central European Time) and 21:00 for Beijing/Hong Kong/Kuala Lumpur. Daylight Saving Time is observed when Central European Summer Time is in effect. 
Watch the mozilla.dev.planning newsgroup | mailing list | Google Group for agendas and other details. 
A brief guide on how to take the Meeting Notes can be found at Writing the Meeting Notes .
